Distribution of food vouchers</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">a) peaceful co-existence between tribal groups and peace prevails
In this instance success will be
&#x2022; 5 interfaith dialogue meetings held
&#x2022; 5 communities have preparedness plans
&#x2022; 20 staff prepared to respond
&#x2022; County coordination response coordinated well 
b) In the event of  conflict timely response to the needs of the affected populations  and contingency plans activated.
&#x2022; 500 HHs targeted with food vouchers 
&#x2022; Protection and safety for women,  girls, children, elderly, disabled and all vulnerable groups.</narrative>
